Django:: Web Development Framework
Advantages ::
1) Fast
2) No of Components are available
3) Security
4) Scalability


to create a DJnago project run the below command
>django-admin startproject django_project(Project_Name)
>cd django_project
django_project>python manage.py runserver

to create a app under u r project run the below command ::
django_project>python manage.py startapp calc(app_name)

// to create a folder to keep all files
django_project>python manage.py collectstatic


//DB Connection
python manage.py makemigrations

python manage.py sqlmigrate travello 0001

python manage.py migrate


